references:
We evaluate the performance of various models on our new benchmark datasets with pseudo GT, OCHuman¬†[70] and LSPet¬†[24].
These datasets have challenging body poses, camera viewpoints, and occlusions.
We found that most models trained on other datasets are struggling in these benchmarks, showing more than 100 m‚Äãmùëöùëömm errors, as shown in table¬†3.
The models trained with pseudo annotations on similar data (training sets of LSPet and OCHuman) show better performance (less than 100 m‚Äãmùëöùëömm).
